SELECT COALESCE(ROUND(COUNT(DISTINCT "requester_id", "accepter_id")/(SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "sender_id", "send_to_id") FROM "FriendRequest"), 2), 0) AS "accept_rate" FROM "RequestAccepted"

SELECT COALESCE(ROUND(COUNT(DISTINCT (CONCAT("requester_id", "accepter_id")))/COUNT(DISTINCT (CONCAT("sender_id", "send_to_id"))), 2), 0) AS "accept_rate" FROM ("FriendRequest") JOIN "RequestAccepted"

SELECT ROUND(COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(1) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "requester_id","accepter_id" FROM "RequestAccepted") AS "A")/(SELECT COUNT(1) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "sender_id","send_to_id" FROM "FriendRequest") AS "B"), 0), 2) AS "accept_rate"

SELECT ROUND(COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(1) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "requester_id","accepter_id" FROM "RequestAccepted") AS "A")/(SELECT COUNT(1) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "sender_id","send_to_id" FROM "FriendRequest") AS "B"), 0), 2) AS "accept_rate"

SELECT ROUND(COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "requester_id", "accepter_id") FROM "RequestAccepted")*1.0/(SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "sender_id", "send_to_id") FROM "FriendRequest"), 0), 2) AS "accept_rate"

SELECT ROUND(COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "requester_id", "accepter_id") FROM "RequestAccepted" AS "a")/(SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "sender_id", "send_to_id") FROM "FriendRequest" AS "b"), 0), 2) AS "accept_rate"

SELECT ROUND(COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(1) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "requester_id","accepter_id" FROM "requestaccepted") AS "A")/(SELECT COUNT(1) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "sender_id","send_to_id" FROM "friendrequest") AS "B"), 0), 2) AS "accept_rate"

SELECT ROUND(COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(1) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "requester_id","accepter_id" FROM "RequestAccepted") AS "A")/(SELECT COUNT(1) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "sender_id","send_to_id" FROM "FriendRequest") AS "F"), 0), 2) AS "accept_rate"
SELECT ROUND(COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "requester_id", "accepter_id") FROM "RequestAccepted")/(SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "sender_id", "send_to_id") FROM "FriendRequest"), 0), 2) AS "accept_rate"

WITH "fr" AS (SELECT "sender_id","send_to_id",MIN("request_date") AS "request_date" FROM "FriendRequest" GROUP BY "sender_id","send_to_id"), "ra" AS (SELECT "requester_id","accepter_id",MIN("accept_date") AS "accept_date" FROM "RequestAccepted" GROUP BY "requester_id","accepter_id") SELECT COALESCE(ROUND("ra_count"."val"/"fr_count"."val", 2), 0.00) AS "accept_rate" FROM (SELECT COUNT(1) AS "val" FROM "ra") AS "ra_count", (SELECT COUNT(1) AS "val" FROM "fr") AS "fr_count"
SELECT ROUND(COALESCE(((SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "requester_id", "accepter_id") FROM "RequestAccepted")/(SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "sender_id", "send_to_id") FROM "FriendRequest")), 0), 2) AS "accept_rate"
SELECT ROUND(COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "requester_id", "accepter_id") FROM "RequestAccepted")/(SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "sender_id", "send_to_id") FROM "FriendRequest"), 0), 2) AS "accept_rate"

SELECT ROUND(COALESCE("q3"."nume"/"q4"."deno", 0.00), 2) AS "accept_rate" FROM (SELECT COUNT(1) AS "nume" FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "requester_id","accepter_id" FROM "RequestAccepted") AS "q1") AS "q3" JOIN (SELECT COUNT(1) AS "deno" FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "sender_id","send_to_id" FROM "FriendRequest") AS "q2") AS "q4"
SELECT ROUND(COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "requester_id", "accepter_id") FROM "RequestAccepted")/(SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT "sender_id", "send_to_id") FROM "FriendRequest"), 0), 2) AS "accept_rate"

WITH "t1" AS (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT CONCAT("requester_id", "accepter_id")) AS "cnt" FROM "requestaccepted"), "t2" AS (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT CONCAT("sender_id", "send_to_id")) AS "cnt" FROM "friendrequest") SELECT ROUND(CASE WHEN "t1"."cnt"=0 THEN 0.00 ELSE "t1"."cnt"/"t2"."cnt" END, 2) AS "accept_rate" FROM ("t1") JOIN "t2"

SELECT COALESCE("result", 0) AS "accept_rate" FROM (SELECT ROUND(COUNT(DISTINCT "requester_id", "accepter_id")/COUNT(DISTINCT "sender_id", "send_to_id"), 2) AS "result" FROM ("FriendRequest") JOIN "RequestAccepted") AS "tmp"

SELECT COALESCE(ROUND((SELECT COUNT(1) AS "n_accept" FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "requester_id","accepter_id" FROM "RequestAccepted") AS "b")/(SELECT COUNT(1) AS "n_request" FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "sender_id","send_to_id" FROM "FriendRequest") AS "a"), 2), 0) AS "accept_rate"

SELECT CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM "FriendRequest" GROUP BY "sender_id","send_to_id") AS "tmp")=0 THEN 0 ELSE ROUND(COUNT(1)/(SELECT COUNT(1) FROM (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM "FriendRequest" GROUP BY "sender_id","send_to_id") AS "tmp"), 2) END AS "accept_rate" FROM (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM "RequestAccepted" AS "R1" GROUP BY "R1"."requester_id","R1"."accepter_id") AS "tmp"
SELECT COALESCE(ROUND(COUNT(DISTINCT "requester_id", "accepter_id")/COUNT(DISTINCT "sender_id", "send_to_id"), 2), 0) AS "accept_rate" FROM ("requestaccepted") JOIN "friendrequest"
